    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve your<strong> chicken stock mix </strong>in 250ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[375ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[500ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Once the lamb mixture has started to brown, add the<strong> chicken stock</strong> to the pan and stir to combine</p><p>Reduce the heat to medium and cook, covered, for a further 5 min or until the lamb is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
