    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your<strong> coriander</strong> roughly, including the stalks</p><p>Add your<strong> diced</strong> <strong>apricots</strong> to the pan and cook for a further 1-2 min – this is your <strong>Moroccan-style</strong> <strong>lamb & sweet potato tagine</strong></p><p>Fluff the <strong>softened</strong> <strong>couscous</strong> with a fork</p>",
